
This test provides environment for testing H48C accelerometer sensor and 
Propeller Demo Board. Run test in simulation mode:

 $ bb --simulation accel.py

Build:

 $ bb build.py

Hardware specifications
-----------------------

Propeller Demo Board --
  http://www.parallax.com/StoreSearchResults/tabid/768/List/0/SortField/4/ProductID/340/Default.aspx

Hitachi H48C Tri-Axis Accelerometer Sensor -- 
  http://www.parallax.com/StoreSearchResults/tabid/768/txtSearch/h48c/List/0/SortField/4/ProductID/97/Default.aspx
 
